r of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe virtue of knowledge is better than the virtue of worship, and the best of your religion is conscientious piety.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 3960 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20534,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/04\/04\/knowledge-over-ibadah\/","url_meta":{"origin":24160,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on &#8216;Ilm: Virtue of knowledge over worship","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 4, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d ibn Abi Waqqas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe virtue of knowledge is more beloved to me than the virtue of worship, and the best of your religion is conscientious piety.\u201d Source: al-A\u0304da\u0304b lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 818 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37943,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/07\/05\/hasan-bored-ibadah\/","url_meta":{"origin":24160,"position":2},"title":"Hasan on Arguing: They were bored with worship, so they argued","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 5, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Ahmad ibn Hanbal reported: Al-Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, heard some people arguing and he said, \u201cBy Allah! These are not but people who are bored with worship and they found speaking easier upon them than acting. Their piety diminished and thus they speak.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd li-Ah\u0323mad\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35027,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/01\/24\/yahya-on-wara\/","url_meta":{"origin":24160,"position":3},"title":"Yahya on Wara\u2019: True piety is inwardly and outwardly","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 24, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn \u2018Alawiyyah reported: Yahya ibn Mu\u2019adh, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cPiety has two types: outward piety and inward piety. As for the external, it is to not make any movement but for the sake of Allah. As for the internal, it is to not allow anything into\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1641,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/11\/27\/best-after-ramadan-muharram\/","url_meta":{"origin":24160,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Best fast after Ramadan is Muharram","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 27, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best prayer after the prescribed prayers is a prayer offered in the middle of the night. The best fast after the month of Ramadan is fasting in the month of Allah, al-Muharram.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":743,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/04\/30\/islam-is-easy\/","url_meta":{"origin":24160,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Religion: Islam is easy, extremism will overwhelm you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 30, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the religion is easy and no one burdens himself in religion but that it overwhelms him. Follow the right course, seek closeness to Allah, give glad tidings, and seek help for worship in the morning and evening\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/24160","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=24160"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/24160\/revisions"}